title: 1 Acre Off the Beaten Path 00 Cable Lane, Hiouchi
text:
1 Acre Off the Beaten Path 00 Cable Lane, Hiouchi ad date: 10/17/2015 
Desirable 1 acre in Hiouchi, CA. Property is ready to build your custom home with water and perk on file. Cleared and partially fenced. A rare find in Hiouchi. Just a short distance to ocean beaches and the pristine Smith River. Small community airport just 20 minutes away. Seller will consider owner carry terms. MLS 1500541 $149,000
